@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### Student: Create Complaint (with image)
POST {{baseUrl}}/complaints/
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebKitFormBoundary

--WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Light not working
--WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Bulb fused in room 101
--WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="issue.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample/issue.jpg
--WebKitFormBoundary--

### Student: My Complaints
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/my
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

### Student: Complaint Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/{{COMPLAINT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

### Student: Complaint Timeline
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/{{COMPLAINT_ID}}/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

### Student: Give Feedback
POST {{baseUrl}}/complaints/{{COMPLAINT_ID}}/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "feedback": "Issue resolved quickly, thanks!",
  "rating": 5
}

### Admin: All Complaints
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: Complaint Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/admin/{{COMPLAINT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: Update Complaint Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/complaints/admin/{{COMPLAINT_ID}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved"
}

### Admin: Complaint Timeline
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/admin/{{COMPLAINT_ID}}/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: AI Config
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/admin/ai/config
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: Update AI Config
PUT {{baseUrl}}/complaints/admin/ai/config
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enabled": true
}

### Admin: AI Quick Setup
POST {{baseUrl}}/complaints/admin/ai/quick-setup
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: AI Toggle
POST {{baseUrl}}/complaints/admin/ai/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Warden: Create Complaint
POST {{baseUrl}}/complaints/warden
Authorization: Bearer {{WARDEN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebKitFormBoundary

--WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Broken window in corridor
--WebKitFormBoundary--

### Warden: Complaints
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/warden
Authorization: Bearer {{WARDEN_TOKEN}}

### Principal: Complaints
GET {{baseUrl}}/complaints/principal
Authorization: Bearer {{PRINCIPAL_TOKEN}}


